---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Telecom Tower Battery Backup — Solar-Hybrid VRLA Solutions"
  description="Solar-hybrid telecom tower backup using AltusVolt 6-CNF VRLA gel batteries. For remote-site backup banks paired with solar PV arrays. Stationary VRLA for grid-tied sites currently not in our catalog."
>
  <nav class="bg-neutral-50 border-b border-neutral-200" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-3">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-steel">Home</a></li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300">/</li>
        <li><a href="/solutions" class="hover:text-steel">Applications</a></li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300">/</li>
        <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Telecom Tower</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="relative w-full h-[420px] flex items-center bg-brand-dark overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img src="/images/hero/hero-solar.webp" alt="Solar-hybrid telecom tower" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-85" width="2000" height="1000" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-dark/90 via-brand-dark/30 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-brand-gold font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-5 pl-3 border-l-2 border-brand-gold">Industries / Telecom Tower</p>
        <h1 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">Solar-Hybrid Telecom Backup</h1>
        <p class="text-[#bbc7df] text-lg md:text-xl font-light leading-relaxed">For remote, off-grid, and solar-hybrid telecom sites in Africa, Southeast Asia, and Latin America. We provide the deep-cycle VRLA gel battery side of the system — pair with your existing solar / hybrid infrastructure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-steel mb-3">Where We Fit</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-brand-dark tracking-tight mb-6">Solar-Hybrid Remote Sites</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our 6-CNF gel battery platform is engineered for the duty cycle of remote telecom sites running on solar-hybrid power — daily cycling under tropical conditions, partial-state-of-charge tolerance, and 12-year float life at 25°C.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            For grid-tied sites with traditional float-only stationary VRLA banks (large central banks for cell towers in urban areas), we recommend specialized telecom VRLA suppliers — that segment is dominated by tier-one Western brands and is not currently in our catalog.
          </p>
          <a href="/products/solar-storage" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-gold hover:text-brand-dark font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
            View 6-CNF Solar Series
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cold-white p-8 rounded-sm">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Right For</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand-gold">✓</span> Remote off-grid cell sites (BTS) in Africa, SE Asia, LatAm</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand-gold">✓</span> Solar-hybrid sites with daily PSoC cycling</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand-gold">✓</span> Microwave repeater stations with 12V or 24V banks</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brand-gold">✓</span> 4–48 hour autonomy designs (small-to-medium banks)</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Not Right For</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-500">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-neutral-400">✗</span> Urban grid-tied 200Ah+ central VRLA banks (use specialized telecom suppliers)</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-neutral-400">✗</span> -48VDC float-only banks (we don't manufacture this format)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-brand-dark py-16">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Need solar-hybrid sizing help?</h2>
        <p class="text-[#bbc7df]">Engineers will size battery banks for your tower load + autonomy + solar input.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/distributor-program?ref=telecom" class="bg-brand-gold text-brand-dark px-8 py-4 font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase rounded-sm hover:brightness-110 transition shrink-0">
        Request Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
